(297, 80, 167, 'nikola7383', 'Technobank 2013', '<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Technobank 2013. konferencija i izlo≈æba bankarske tehnologije</strong>&nbsp;odr≈æaƒáe se 1<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">0. i 11. aprila u hotelu Metropol Palace u Beogradu</strong>. Ovogodi&scaron;nji&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Technobank ƒáe se&nbsp;</strong>fokusirati na najnovije raspolo≈æive tehnologije u regionu i &scaron;ire i njihovoj primeni na ovim tr≈æi&scaron;tima. Takoƒëe, ovogodi&scaron;nje teme ƒáe se baviti i novim uƒçesnicima na platnom tr≈æi&scaron;tu &ndash; kao &scaron;to su mobilni operateri ili veliki maloprodajni lanci. Na konferenciji ƒáe uƒçestvovati eksperti iz zemlje i inostranstva koji ƒáe ponuditi prezentacije najnovijih re&scaron;enja kao i studije sluƒçaja u oblasti novih platnih tehnologija.</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	Najnovije tehnologije, kao &scaron;to su NFC beskontaktne tehnologije, kori&scaron;ƒáenje mobilnog telefona kao sredstva plaƒáanja, sistemi javnog prevoza, lojalti &scaron;eme, primena prepaid kartica, cloud computing i nova dokument-menad≈æment re&scaron;enja ƒáe biti prezentovane tokom rada Konferencije. I ove godine&nbsp;specijalizovani forum -&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">CARD FORUM &amp; EXPO 2013</strong>, potpuno posveƒáen platnim transakcijama putem bankarskih kartica i podr≈æanim ICT tehnologijama u Evropi i svetu, biƒáe odr≈æan tokom Technobank Konferencije.</p>\n<h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-size: 25px; font-family: muzeo, ''Trebuchet MS'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n	<cufon alt="Agenda" class="cufon cufon-canvas" style="width: 90px; height: 25px; display: inline-block !important; position: relative !important; vertical-align: middle !important; font-size: 1px !important; line-height: 1px !important;"><canvas height="28" style="position: relative !important; width: 102px; height: 28px; top: -3px; left: -1px;" width="102"></canvas><cufontext style="display: inline-block !important; width: 0px !important; height: 0px !important; overflow: hidden !important; text-indent: -10000in !important;"></cufontext></cufon></h2>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Technobank 2013 Konferencije</strong></p>\n<ul style="margin: 0px 0px 15px 12px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 12px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 17px;">\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Business Continuity Management (BCM) &ndash; Business Continuity Planning (BCP) i Disaster Recovery (DR)</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Upravljanje poslovnim procesima</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Raƒçunarstvo u oblacima (Cloud Computing)</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Dru&scaron;tvene mre≈æe</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Data centri</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Mobilna telefonija ƒçetvrte generacije</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Mobline aplikacije u poslovanju</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Upravljanje rizicima i naplata potra≈æivanja</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Identity and Access Management sistemi</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Customer Relationship Management (CRM) and Contact Center (CC) technologies</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		Digitalno arhiviranje i sistemi upravljanja dokumentacijom</li>\n	<li style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">\n		ICT bezbednosni aspekti u bankama</li>\n	<li style