(300, 80, 168, 'nikola7383', 'WebDan konferencija', '<p>\n	&nbsp;</p>\n<p style="margin: 0px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); line-height: 18px;">\n	<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">WebDan</strong>&nbsp;je&nbsp;besplatna&nbsp;jednodnevna konferencija koja ƒáe se odr≈æati&nbsp;<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">13. aprila u Boru</strong>, u sali muziƒçke &scaron;kole od 11h.<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;">Konferencija je posveƒáena internetu, zaradi preko interneta i pokretanju web biznisa</strong>. Namenjena je pre svega srednjo&scaron;kolcima i studentima, ali i svima onima koji ≈æele da im web postane posao. Zanimljivi predavaƒçi prenosiƒáe svoja znanja i iskustva u radu na nekim od najpopularnijih i najzanimljivijih web sajtova u Srbiji.</p>\n<div id="predavaci" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: ''Times New Roman''; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); line-height: 16px;">\n	<h2 style="margin: 25px 0px 15px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-weight: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-size: 25px; font-family: muzeo, ''Trebuchet MS'', Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68);">\n		<cufon alt="Predavaƒçi" class="cufon cufon-canvas" style="width: 114px; height: 25px; display: inline-block !important; position: relative !important; vertical-align: middle !important; font-size: 1px !important; line-height: 1px !important;"><canvas height="28" style="position: relative !important; width: 133px; height: 28px; top: -3px; left: -1px;" width="1